Taketha LOVEST, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
David MANGIERO, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1610 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 06, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SUAREZ and FERNANDEZ, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
